snippet.title: OFFICIAL THE DIVISION 2 - ENTER THE DARK ZONE TRAILER
snippet.description:
Cross the Dark Zone Gates...
Take on other players, friends or foes, and prove your combat proficiency.

Tom Clancy's The Division 2 - OUT 15.03.19 on PC, Xbox One and PS4.

Preorder the Phoenix Shield Collector's Edition and start your mission on March 12th, 3 days before everyone else!
http://thedivisiongame.com/preorder

Tom Clancy’s The Division 2 is an online open-world, action shooter RPG experience.

Join us now:
Website : http://thedivisiongame.com
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/TheDivisionGameUK/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/TheDivisionGame
